Detailed Description

cvmx_rfif_eth_rx::_ecc_info

These registers capture details about the first ECC error encountered for the given RX Ethernet RAM. The values are held until the error bit is cleared in the RFIF_ETH_ECC_ERR register. When that occurs, the captured info is cleared, and the info register will capture the details about the next ECC error.
